description: The grade result the student achieved on the exam
Endorsements are generally only speaking endorsements in language courses and are optional. Most students will not have an endorsement and this will be blank.
The grade result the student achieved on the endorsement where applicable
The level at which the exam was taken
The Cambridge AICE Diploma is a group certificate that is awarded on a points system. Distinction: 360-420 points; Merit: 250-359 points; Pass: 140-249 points.
